This delicious and wholesome Thai spicy chilli and basil rice dish is the perfect midweek meal to prepare on a cloudy and slightly chilly day to warm your belly and put a smile on your face.  If you are not a fan of rice, then you can enjoy the spicy Thai chilli dish with your favourite baked or store bought bread or flatbread.  ALSO TRY: Recipe of the day: Yummy guilt-free potato bake This recipe was found on delicious.co.au